reviewText: Opened the disk, put it in the player, only got  black screen.....what a piece of junk.....don't waste your money.....
Great picture & sound quality. Best movie ever! Probably my 10th viewing of it.

first class transfer and quality, plays perfectly, only minus, liner notes only in italian.
